/td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  ACSI<a name=\"procedure-category-314e-ACSI\"> </a></td><td>Advanced Cross-Sectional</td><td>CT Scans, MRIs</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  CATH<a name=\"procedure-category-314e-CATH\"> </a></td><td>Interventional Radiology &amp; Cath Lab Imaging</td><td>Angiography, Fluoroscopy</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  NUCM<a name=\"procedure-category-314e-NUCM\"> </a></td><td>Nuclear Medicine</td><td>PET Scans, SPECT Scans, Bone Scintigraphy</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  MEDP<a name=\"procedure-category-314e-MEDP\"> </a></td><td>Medical Photography</td><td>Dermatology, Ophthalmology retinal photos</td></tr><tr><td>1</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">FNP<a name=\"procedure-category-314e-FNP\"> </a></td><td>Functional &amp; Physiological Studies (Non-Invasive)</td><td>Functional and physiological diagnostic procedures</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  CARD<a name=\"procedure-category-314e-CARD\"> </a></td><td>Cardiology</td><td>EKGs, Holter monitors, Stress tests</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  NEUS<a name=\"procedure-category-314e-NEUS\"> </a></td><td>Neurology &amp; Sleep</td><td>EEGs, EMGs, Polysomnography</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  PULM<a name=\"procedure-category-314e-PULM\"> </a></td><td>Pulmonary</td><td>PFTs, Spirometry, Blood Gas tracings</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  AUDV<a name=\"procedure-category-314e-AUDV\"> </a></td><td>Audiology &amp; Vestibular</td><td>Audiograms, Tympanometry, VNG balance tests</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  GIFN<a name=\"procedure-category-314e-GIFN\"> </a></td><td>Gastroenterology Functional</td><td>Manometry, 24-hr pH monitoring</td></tr><tr><td>1</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">SUR<a name=\"procedure-category-314e-SUR\"> </a></td><td>Invasive &amp; Surgical Procedures</td><td>Invasive and surgical clinical procedures</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  ORSU<a name=\"procedure-category-314e-ORSU\"> </a></td><td>Operative &amp; Major Surgical Procedures</td><td>OR surgeries, day surgeries</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  ENDO<a name=\"procedure-category-314e-ENDO\"> </a></td><td>Endoscopic Procedures</td><td>GI scopes, Bronchoscopy, Cystoscopy</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  MSUR<a name=\"procedure-category-314e-MSUR\"> </a></td><td>Bedside &amp; Minor Invasive Procedures</td><td>Lumbar punctures, Paracentesis</td></tr><tr><td>1</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">TIN<a name=\"procedure-category-314e-TIN\"> </a></td><td>Therapeutics &amp; Infusion Services</td><td>Therapeutic and infusion-based treatment services</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  IONC<a name=\"procedure-category-314e-IONC\"> </a></td><td>Infusion Oncology</td><td>Chemotherapy, Immunotherapy biologics</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  RONC<a name=\"procedure-category-314e-RONC\"> </a></td><td>Radiation Oncology</td><td>External beam radiation, Brachytherapy</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  BLDT<a name=\"procedure-category-314e-BLDT\"> </a></td><td>Renal &amp; Blood Therapies</td><td>Hemodialysis, Peritoneal dialysis, Apheresis</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  INFU<a name=\"procedure-category-314e-INFU\"> </a></td><td>Specialty Infusions</td><td>IV Antibiotics, Iron infusions, Pain pumps</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  MEDA<a name=\"procedure-category-314e-MEDA\"> </a></td><td>Bedside &amp; General Medication Administration</td><td>General medication administration activities</td></tr><tr><td>1</td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">RHB<a name=\"procedure-category-314e-RHB\"> </a></td><td>Rehabilitative, Supportive &amp; Physical Medicine</td><td>Rehabilitative and su